Single serving site based upon Yahoo! weather report for Belfast:

http://weather.yahoo.com/northern-ireland/belfast/belfast-44544


Run bin/update_forecast.rb to fetch the current weather condition

Example crontab syntax to have the weather updated every hour:

0 * * * * /var/www/isitraininginbelfast.com/bin/update_forecast.rb


To run the Sinatra app:

rackup ./config.ru -p 9000

Browse to:

http://0.0.0.0:9000/
